Seolsong High School

260
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:43,000
Scrub it well.

261
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:47,410
Scrub it well as atonement for your wrongdoing with intentions toward a transparent life.

262
00:20:47,410 --> 00:20:48,920
I'm going to check later.

263
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:51,760
Okay, Teacher.

264
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:18,300
You are working hard for service, Bok Soo.

265
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:20,450
Hello, Teacher. Good morning.

266
00:21:20,450 --> 00:21:23,930
It's me. Ma Yeong Joon.

267
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:26,620
Ah, yes, I know. The English teacher.

268
00:21:26,620 --> 00:21:35,140
Uh, perhaps, were you there when I was in school? I'm very sorry if I wasn't thinking... no, don't recognize you.

269
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:38,270
Look at me carefully. It's me.

270
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:52,380
Bread shuttle?!

271
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:06,200
The class shuttle (errand runner)? Ma Yeong Joon?

272
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,570
I'm so happy to see you again, friend.

273
00:22:08,570 --> 00:22:11,790
Thank you for remembering me.

274
00:22:11,790 --> 00:22:14,510
- We were close friends, right?
- Right, Bok Soo.

275
00:22:14,510 --> 00:22:18,190
Before, you helped me out a lot. Now, I will help you

276
00:22:18,190 --> 00:22:21,630
since I am a teacher, and you are a student.

277
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:26,250
Okay.

278
00:22:28,300 --> 00:22:29,940
Do a good job.

279
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:46,520
This activity is designed to train your mind

280
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:49,410
by repeatedly doing a simple task.

281
00:22:49,410 --> 00:22:51,400
I want you to carefully focus on

282
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:55,070
what you guys did wrong.

283
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,700
Man! I really don't think I can do this!

284
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:01,390
This takes a lot more energy than it looks like.

285
00:23:01,390 --> 00:23:02,860
Why do I have to do this?

286
00:23:02,860 --> 00:23:05,540
Because we're full of mileage.

287
00:23:05,540 --> 00:23:06,450
Mileage?

288
00:23:06,450 --> 00:23:09,390
Elder, you don't know about mileage.

289
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:11,450
It's negative points as a student.

290
00:23:13,230 --> 00:23:15,100
What's with your hair?

291
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:19,370
- Just stop taking pictures! If I become famous, will you take responsibility?
- You're ugly.

292
00:23:19,370 --> 00:23:21,600
What are you talking about? My mom says I'm the most handsome.

293
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:24,180
You still don't know that she's fibbing?

294
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,080
What is this image again?

295
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:39,550
The legendary attention whoring student in Seolsong High is entering the Wildflower class.

296
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:44,130
Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!

297
00:23:44,130 --> 00:23:45,150
What are you doing?

298
00:23:45,150 --> 00:23:48,240
Starting today, I am in the Wildflower class.

299
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:51,570
Were you kicked out of the Ivy class?

300
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:55,600
Hey! Then shouldn't you go to Sky class? Why are you here? Is it because you don't know where you are?

301
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:59,670
Wildflowers are pretty.

302
00:23:59,670 --> 00:24:00,820
What'd you say?

303
00:24:00,820 --> 00:24:02,590
- I can sit here, right?
- Uh-uh!

304
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:04,820
I didn't give you permission yet.

305
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:09,630
Between us? What do you mean "permission"?

306
00:24:09,630 --> 00:24:10,980
What is the relationship between us?

307
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:13,440
Best friends.

308
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:19,420
Friend? Hey! I am nine years older than you! "Friends?"
(In Korea, "friend" is usually used for people born the same year.)

309
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:22,220
You'd better call me, "Hyung."

310
00:24:22,220 --> 00:24:23,790
Yes.

311
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:29,350
Okay. Everyone go to your seats.

312
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:41,400
- What are you doing, Oh Yeong Min? Class is starting. Go to your classroom.
- Ma'am?

313
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:44,560
Teacher, you must not have heard yet. I have moved to the Wildflower class.

314
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:46,060
What?

315
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:48,520
Why here? You should go to the Sky class.

316
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:53,530
I cannot go up by my own effort. Please allow me to go down by my own free will.

317
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,580
Where did Seung Woo go?

318
00:24:59,580 --> 00:25:01,630
He hasn't arrived yet?

319
00:25:01,630 --> 00:25:03,290
He's tardy. Did you call him?

320
00:25:03,290 --> 00:25:04,430
He doesn't answer.

321
00:25:04,430 --> 00:25:06,770
If he comes, tell him to come see me.

322
00:25:06,770 --> 00:25:09,690
Okay. Let's not be causing any trouble.

323
00:25:09,690 --> 00:25:11,670
Get ready for class.

324
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:15,890
Oh Yeong Min. Come out and see me for a moment.

325
00:25:15,890 --> 00:25:17,810
Hey! Like I was saying...

326
00:25:17,810 --> 00:25:20,620
I know what you're thinking, but

327
00:25:20,620 --> 00:25:27,140
Yeong Min, the lesson level of this class is not your academic level. In addition, this class does not receive school support.

328
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:29,230
This is a battlefield.

329
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:33,630
This is a different atmosphere than you are used to. This place is more hardcore than the Ivy class.

330
00:25:33,630 --> 00:25:36,900
However, I have comrades here.

331
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:38,130
What?

332
00:25:38,130 --> 00:25:39,890
I'm not lonely.

333
00:25:39,890 --> 00:25:44,330
If I bleed while fighting, there will be someone to put a band-aid on me.

334
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:49,780
If I fall behind, I have a platoon captain to help me.

335
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:54,850
Please quickly add me to the class roster.

336
00:26:04,210 --> 00:26:08,260
What? Looking at this menu makes you want to go back to the Ivy class, huh?

337
00:26:08,260 --> 00:26:10,880
Now you really regret that you came on your own two feet.

338
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:13,610
This is a grass field (full of vegetables, usually for the poor). It's healthy food.

339
00:26:13,610 --> 00:26:15,870
You're happy with it! Go.

340
00:26:15,870 --> 00:26:17,750
Go.

341
00:26:29,340 --> 00:26:31,740
Okay.Thank you for the— Agh!

342
00:26:34,470 --> 00:26:36,430
Are you crazy? Why are you here?

343
00:26:36,430 --> 00:26:38,390
Are you crazy?

344
00:26:38,390 --> 00:26:40,450
I already told you I was coming to the school.

345
00:26:40,450 --> 00:26:42,610
Even still. With that determination, go do something else.

346
00:26:42,610 --> 00:26:46,530
Something else? To me, you are my everything.

347
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:48,790
The company. What about the company?

348
00:26:48,790 --> 00:26:52,190
If you are not there, there is no company.

349
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,770
Really!

350
00:26:56,770 --> 00:27:00,870
Eat well. From now on, I will take care of your meals.

351
00:27:00,870 --> 00:27:04,360
Noona, can't you take care of your own life? Why on earth are you here?

352
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:08,460
What are talking about? I am here to take care of you, Kang Bok Soo.

353
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:10,150
That's why I'm here.

354
00:27:17,390 --> 00:27:19,160
Eat.

355
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:21,790
Please give me some pork cutlet.

356
00:27:33,100 --> 00:27:35,190
May I have a little.

357
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,990
Can I have a little more?

358
00:27:40,990 --> 00:27:42,940
Thank you.

359
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:49,060
May—

360
00:27:49,060 --> 00:27:52,050
You still have a good appetite.

361
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:06,950
So you are still lying? You are quite good at that.

362
00:28:06,950 --> 00:28:10,760
Right! You are really good at feeding us yeot (Korean candy/sounds similar to feeding BS).

363
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,540
Hey! Yang Min Ji! What did I lie—

364
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:14,580
Now, I will really not let you off.

365
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:19,280
If you hurt Kang Bok Soo again, I will certainly kill you!

366
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,440
Who are you?

367
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:26,980
Me? I'm Bok Soo's companion. I've been with him for nine years.

368
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,840
So?

369
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:33,280
Do you know how Bok Soo has been living all this time?

370
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:35,300
Do I have to know?

371
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:40,020
Wow! You are still an a**hole.

372
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:44,520
I like your attitude. From now on, don't ever get curious about Bok Soo.

373
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:48,740
That should be fine since I will always be by Bok Soo's side.

374
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:03,550
You have to bury the evidence for the perfect crime.

375
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:06,390
Amateurs. They've got a long way to go.

376
00:29:06,390 --> 00:29:08,930
Do better. Kids. Ew!

377
00:29:12,490 --> 00:29:14,730
Bok Soo!

378
00:29:14,730 --> 00:29:16,190
Ah, you startled me!

379
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,900
What are you doing?

380
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:20,860
Noona, you really know how to surprise someone. Oh, my heart.

381
00:29:20,860 --> 00:29:22,340
I'm cleaning up.

382
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:27,340
Really? I hear that your heart raced because of me.

383
00:29:28,090 --> 00:29:33,870
Noona. You can interpret freely, but you are too much of a free spirit.

384
00:29:34,910 --> 00:29:38,290
But what is that? A new accessory?

385
00:29:38,290 --> 00:29:40,210
- Hold still for a sec.
- You...

386
00:29:45,130 --> 00:29:50,350
I must have worked very hard. I'm like a professional now.

387
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:07,230
Bok Soo, isn't there something here too?

388
00:30:07,230 --> 00:30:09,850
What are you doing? Ah! Oil—

389
00:30:09,850 --> 00:30:11,540
Did you wash your hair?

390
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:15,120
You must be hygienic since you are now working in the kitchen.

391
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:19,010
Even still. It's only Bok Soo who looks after me.

392
00:30:19,010 --> 00:30:21,640
Thank you. Shall we go see a movie?

393
00:30:23,670 --> 00:30:25,590
Let's go.

394
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:38,180
Consulting Room

395
00:30:57,860 --> 00:31:01,080
Let's write this on your textbook.

396
00:31:03,790 --> 00:31:06,510
Copy. Ready. Begin!

397
00:31:42,630 --> 00:31:44,920
In an old fairy tale, the magpie also repaid kindness for a good deed.

398
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:47,460
The snake and the tiger did the same thing.

399
00:31:47,460 --> 00:31:51,420
But as a human, I must recompense the grace from the teacher.

400
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:53,400
If I don't, I'm less than an animal.

401
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:58,780
I am Kang Bok Soo. I'm the kind of person who cannot live owing a debt to someone.

402
00:32:04,950 --> 00:32:07,790
There is something wrong with my digestion.

403
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:11,100
Did I eat too much cafeteria food?

404
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:16,100
Teacher. I'm being serious.

405
00:32:16,100 --> 00:32:18,800
I didn't say you weren't serious.

406
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:21,580
Who is this who needs medicine?

407
00:32:21,580 --> 00:32:26,020
I said, it's me. My insides are churning. I feel like I'm going to throw up.

408
00:32:26,020 --> 00:32:29,980
If you don't take medication properly, something serious can happen.

409
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:33,670
If something happens, is it okay?

410
00:32:41,110 --> 00:32:43,590
Students looking for medicine on someone else's behalf,

